How To Go Live

Follow these steps to go live

  • 1
    Review
    Please review our technoical documentation here.
  • 2
    Submit
    Once you are satisfied with the documentation, send an email to partnerships@buypower.ng and include the following:
    • The website URL to be integrated.
    • Valid IDs of Directors.
    • Acopy of your CAC certificate.
    • Contact number
  • 3
    Agreement
    After receiving your email, our merchant agreement contract and Commercials will be shared with you for your review and execution.
  • 4
    Integration
    A Skype link will be created for you to join our Developer Community to ensure a smooth integration process.
  • 5
    Go Live
    Your Go Live account will be created once Sandbox integration is completed and you will have an onboarding session with our Partnership Team.
